import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { placesFunction } from 'src/app/welcomemenu.js'; import { MyData } from 'src/app/mydata'; import { Place } from '../../models/place.model'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-places', templateUrl: './places.component.html', styleUrls: ['./places.component.css'] }) export class PlacesComponent implements OnInit { place: Place[] = []; constructor(private http: HttpClient, private myData: MyData) { } ngOnInit() { this.myData.getPlaces().subscribe((data: any[]) => { this.place = data; }); } }
